Package: abSan
Type: Package
Title: Computes the Abreu-Sannikov repeated game algorithm
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-08-27
Author: Philip Barrett
Maintainer: Philip Barrett <pobarrett@uchicago.edu>
Description: Code to solve repeated games using the method described in 
    Abreu & Sannikov's 2013 Theoretical Economics paper "An algorithm for 
    two-player games with perfect monitoring"
License: GPL-3
Depends:R (>= 2.15.0), Rcpp (>= 0.10.4), parallel, RcppEigen, RUnit
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
